info.description:
This program converts the XML export of del.icio.us
(http://del.icio.us/api/posts/all)
to a simple HTML page.
Posts are sorted by inverse chronological order.
This is an alternative to del.icio.us standard HTML export.
This program also serves as an example of parsing an XML document with DOM
(minidom).
info.name: delxml2html
info.summary: Converts del.icio.us XML export to an HTML page.
